data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a desirable location, this meticulously maintained house offers a truly remarkable living experience. Prepare to be wowed by the fully equipped outdoor kitchen, perfect for hosting memorable gatherings and enjoying al fresco dining. The large 37x12 deck provides ample space for entertaining, lounging, or simply unwinding while relishing the surrounding views.  Indoors, the primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an upgraded IKEA PAX closet system and brand new carpet.  The game room is equipped with a built-in IKEA entertainment center. Alexa-controlled smart switches throughout home and upgraded smart thermostats.  Fresh neutral paint. Brand new refrigerator, washer, and dryer included.
